<paragraph blockId="32.[151,1437,1714,2027]" box="[151,1072,1714,1739]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183">
This species has not been revised since description and the 
<typeStatus box="[815,913,1714,1739]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183">holotype</typeStatus>
has been lost.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="32.[151,1437,1714,2027]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,662,1750,1775]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183">Translation of the original description</emphasis>
. Subrounded, convex, black, matt; prothorax slightly marked, with arches and whitish pubescence on both sides; elytra with coarse punctuation medially, slightly rugose, with whitish rare pubescence on both sides, wih conic gibbosity and not very angular median region; margin expanded, sparsely punctate. Length. 
<quantity box="[353,448,1858,1883]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.95" pageId="32" pageNumber="183" unit="mm" value="19.5">19.5mm</quantity>
, width 
<quantity box="[530,641,1858,1883]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.825" pageId="32" pageNumber="183" unit="mm" value="18.25">18.25mm</quantity>
. (
<bibRefCitation author="Boheman" box="[659,892,1858,1883]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183" refString="Boheman, C. H. (1850) Monographia Cassididarum I. Officina Nordstedtiana, Holmiae, 452 pp." type="book" year="1850">
Boheman 
<number box="[775,835,1858,1883]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183" value="1850.0">1850</number>
: 
<number box="[845,892,1859,1883]" pageId="32" pageNumber="183" value="229.0">229</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
